A physics-based, thermodynamically sound field theory of semantic memory.

47:15.580 --> 47:20.780
A framework where meaning itself exists as a continuous fluid dynamic.

47:21.340 --> 47:28.260
Where every action from dropping an apple to breaking a window leaves a permanent causal residue on a hypergraph.

